  "original_title": "40,000 \u0bae\u0bc6\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bcd \u0ba4\u0bca\u0ba9\u0bcd \u0baa\u0bc6\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0bb1\u0bcb\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b8f\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0bb1\u0bbf\u0baf \u0b95\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b87\u0ba9\u0bcd\u0bb1\u0bc1 \u0ba8\u0bbe\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bc8 \u0bb5\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0b9f\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "A ship loaded with 40,000 metric tonnes of petrol will arrive in the country today",
      "author": "",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Minister of Power and Energy said that the vessel loaded with 40,000 metric tonnes of petrol will reach the country tonight (22).",
        "Also, the ministry has confirmed that a ship carrying 40,000 metric tons of diesel has arrived in the country yesterday (21) night.",
        "Minister Kanjana Wijesekhara said on Twitter that the National Fuel Pass QR system will be implemented nationwide from Monday, July 25.",
        "He further informed that the QR code will be tested in several places in Colombo from July 21 to 24.",
        "As notified by the Ministry of Power, if the last digit of the vehicle number plate is 0,1 and 2 then for those vehicles Tuesday and Saturday, if the number 3,4 and 5 is Thursday and Sunday, if the number is 6,7,8 and 9 then Monday, Wednesday and Fuel will also be distributed on Fridays."
      ],
